---
export const prerender = false;
---
<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="pt-BR">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8" />
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0" />
  <title>Página Indisponível — Nemes & Teibel</title>
  <meta name="robots" content="noindex, nofollow" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.googleapis.com" />
  <link rel="preconnect" href="https://fonts.gstatic.com" crossorigin />
  <link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=DM+Sans:wght@400;500;600&family=Playfair+Display:wght@600;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet" />
  <style>
    *, *::before, *::after { box-sizing: border-box; margin: 0; padding: 0; }
    body {
      font-family: 'DM Sans', system-ui, sans-serif;
      background: #F0EDE6;
      min-height: 100vh;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      padding: 1.5rem;
      color: #3D3828;
    }
    .card {
      text-align: center;
      max-width: 460px;
    }
    .icon {
      width: 64px;
      height: 64px;
      background: #fff;
      border-radius: 50%;
      display: flex;
      align-items: center;
      justify-content: center;
      margin: 0 auto 1.5rem;
      box-shadow: 0 4px 16px rgba(58,52,38,0.1);
    }
    .icon svg { color: #B8972A; }
    h1 {
      font-family: 'Playfair Display', serif;
      font-size: 1.6rem;
      color: #3A3426;
      font-weight: 700;
      margin-bottom: 0.75rem;
    }
    p {
      font-size: 0.95rem;
      color: #9A9285;
      line-height: 1.6;
      margin-bottom: 2rem;
    }
    .btn {
      display: inline-flex;
      align-items: center;
      gap: 0.4rem;
      background: #3A3426;
      color: #F5F0E8;
      text-decoration: none;
      padding: 0.75rem 1.75rem;
      border-radius: 50px;
      font-family: 'DM Sans', sans-serif;
      font-size: 0.9rem;
      font-weight: 600;
      transition: background 0.2s;
    }
    .btn:hover { background: #4a4132; }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="card">
    <div class="icon">
      <svg width="28" height="28" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5">
        <path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M12 9v3.75m9-.75a9 9 0 11-18 0 9 9 0 0118 0zm-9 3.75h.008v.008H12v-.008z" />
      </svg>
    </div>
    <h1>Página temporariamente indisponível</h1>
    <p>
      Esta página está em manutenção ou foi desativada temporariamente.
      Por favor, volte mais tarde ou acesse nosso site principal.
    </p>
    <a href="/" class="btn">
      <svg width="16" height="16" viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="2"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" d="M10.5 19.5L3 12m0 0l7.5-7.5M3 12h18"/></svg>
      Ir para o site
    </a>
  </div>
</body>
</html>
